Product description

FABRIC

  • Made of water-resistant nylon and the interior is lined (machine washable).
  • Note: Accessories are not included.

FUNCTIONAL POCKETS


  • A front pocket (which could be separated into 2 parts by the inner hooks & loops fastener).
  • 4 side open pockets to store tools like cooking tongs and basting brushes.


  • A top handle (reinforced stitches) for taking off the cover easily.


  • Inner soft padding helps this cover retain its shape when not covering the indoor grill.

SUITABLE MODELS


  • NOTE: It is a cover with pocket. No bottom.


  • SUITABLE MODELS: Compatible with Ninja* FG551 Foodi Smart XL 6-in-1 Indoor Grill. *Luxja cover isn't associated with the above brand.
